msgstr "[vector]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:374
msgid ""
"Specify the vector file to export the data to. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specificeer het vectorbestand waarnaar de gegevens moeten worden "
"geëxporteerd. :ref:`Een van <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudconversion.rst:424
msgid ""
"Output vector layer features of the point cloud layer are exported to. "
"Currently supported format is :file:`.GPKG`."
msgstr ""
"Uitvoer vectorlaag waar de objecten van de laag puntenwolk naartoe zijn "
"geëxporteerd. Momenteel ondersteunde indeling is :file:`.GPKG`."

